                              'Angolos' 1.02

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'Angolos' is a Workbench @{" game " link play} played on an hexagonal-shaped board,
the idea is to link all the tiles on the board and return to the
starting tile and by doing so, make the biggest number of angles
(links that are not at 180 degres from one to another).

  Have fun!

